OL,6,FThe UK Government's plans for have
OL,7,Fbeen criticised as a "misuse" of power
OL,8,Ffor trying to undermine proposals for
OL,9,Fits own scheme.
OL,11,FIt mirrors a similar row with the
OL,12,FScottish Government which later backed
OL,13,Fdown and centres on whether or not
OL,14,Fglass should be included in the
OL,15,Fschemes.
