OL,3,CWelsh and UK Government row over
OL,4,Cplanned deposit return scheme
OL,6,FIn a written statement, the UK
OL,7,FEnvironment minister said that his
OL,8,Fgovernment intends to use post-Brexit
OL,9,Fpowers effectively to limit the amount
OL,10,Fof glass being included in a Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment DRS.
OL,13,FBut the Welsh Government says it will
OL,14,Fpush ahead with its plans and has
OL,15,Fcondemned the UK Government for
OL,16,Fattempting to "impose its policy on
OL,17,Fdevolved governments."
