OL,3,CWelsh and UK Government row over
OL,4,Cplanned deposit return scheme
OL,6,FThe latest clash between the two
OL,7,Fgovernments comes as the UK Government
OL,8,Fannounced details of its plans to
OL,9,Fintroduce a Deposit Return Scheme
OL,10,F(DRS) for drinks containers.
OL,12,FIt will in effect be several schemes
OL,13,Fbecause many of the powers involved
OL,14,Fare devolved to Wales, Scotland and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,17,FWhile the governments agree on most
OL,18,Faspects of the schemes, there has been
OL,19,Fa standoff when it comes to including
OL,20,Fglass containers.
