OL,3,CWelsh and UK Government row over
OL,4,Cplanned deposit return scheme
OL,6,FThe UK Minister Robin Moore said that
OL,7,F"It remains my view that including
OL,8,Fglass in any UK DRS will create undue
OL,9,Fcomplexity for the drinks industry and
OL,10,Fit increases storage and handling
OL,11,Fcosts for retailers."
OL,13,FFollowing a previous argument, the
OL,14,FScottish Government has agreed to
OL,15,Fexclude glass from its scheme in order
OL,16,Fto make sure its overall plans can go
OL,17,Fforward.
OL,19,FHowever, the Welsh Government has said
OL,20,Fit will include glass along with
OL,21,Fplastic, aluminium and steel.
