OL,7,FChange and Rural Affairs Secretary,
OL,8,FHuw Irranca-Davies, said that he was
OL,9,Fpleased that schemes in Wales,
OL,10,FEngland, Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fwould be broadly similar and be
OL,12,Fintroduced at the same time in October
OL,13,F2027.
