OL,6,FThe use of those UKIM powers will have
OL,7,Fthe effect of limiting the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment's plan. No bottles or other
OL,9,Fcontainers made outside Wales will be
OL,10,Fpart of the Welsh Deposit Return
OL,11,FScheme.
OL,13,FIn an interview with me, Huw Irranca-
OL,14,FDavies denied that by digging its
OL,15,Fheels in, the Welsh Government risks
OL,16,Fmaking Wales an outlier when the
OL,17,Fschemes are introduced.
