OL,6,FHe said that "It's not Wales that's
OL,7,Fthe outlier. Only a couple of years
OL,8,Fago, we had signed off across the four
OL,9,Fnations on a scheme that would include
OL,10,Fglass, it would be the all in schemes.
OL,12,F"The outlier at this moment in time is
OL,13,FEngland; Scotland want to proceed with
OL,14,Fglass as do we because we're on a
OL,15,Fdifferent part of the journey. And I
OL,16,Fsuspect colleagues in Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fare interested in doing this approach
OL,18,Fas well.
